U = \left\{ \begin{pmatrix} a & -b \\ \overline{b} & \overline{a} \end{pmatrix} \in GL(2, \mathbb{C}) \bigg\vert |a|^2 + |b|^2 = 1, \ a,b \in \mathbb{C} \right\} \subset (GL(2,\mathbb{C}), \cdot)
|a|^2 + |b|^2 = 1
|a'|^2 + |b'|^2 = 1
